"hoti, na suppaṭippassaddho, opakkamikā cepi te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā dukkhā "
"tibbā kharā kaṭukā vedanā vedayanti, abhabbāva te ñāṇāya dassanāya "
"anuttarāya sambodhāya."
msgstr ""
